    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-31T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-31T11:00:00-05:00" n="660"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d660">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">832.61333/903: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Counselor of Embassy in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Simmons</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-31T13:00:00-03:00"
                            >December 31, 1943—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 5:04 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5957. The Embassy will delay presentation of note (Department’s 4637, December
                    20, 12 p.m.) until we reach an understanding with the Brazilians on the ship
                    deal. Rich agrees.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Simmons</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
